{"tid":1490733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個藍老母","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:01:03.000Z","uid":257890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc44ba885f56f2452e418a8243de1981b43c4cd","tid":1490733,"uid":257890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"講返背景先 全家都係黃 除左個仆街老母 佢之前話自己唔係藍絲 只係會幫啱嗰邊 但佢全部幫哂藍絲 簡單黎講即係佢係藍色 <br />\n琴晚有單斬人案 今朝我地全家喺道傾 <br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:死啦一陣出街會唔會比人斬 好驚啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:痴線 無啦啦點會比人斬呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:吓但嗰個女仔係無啦啦比人斬喎(我已經㷫過火屎)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:你好人好者點會比人斬呀 冇人叫你行連儂隧道嫁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:而家就係乜人都斬呀 斬埋你添呀<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以救下我 衰啲講句 最好佢快啲比人斬 食催淚彈 食椒"},{"pid":"4adf5e51c964a7610dbe35b6672fa2a72a24d310","tid":1490733,"uid":291656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06f7139e74fd5c973938474d66cd0d172e46b1ba","tid":1490733,"uid":208285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"同你講聲唔好意思先<br />\n我而家立即屌你老母"},{"pid":"8356a859b31823af110ea05039aa3ba20368b32d","tid":1490733,"uid":272178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}